sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    User->>Browser: Interacts with SPA interface
    Browser->>Browser: User writes note content
    Browser->>Browser: User clicks 'Save' button
    Browser->>Browser: Validate note content
    Browser->>Browser: Create JSON object with note content
    Browser->>Server: POST request to create new note
    activate Server
    Server-->>Browser: 200 OK (Note created successfully)
    deactivate Server
    Browser->>Browser: Update UI to display new note
